on with ME/CFS has to rely on out of area referrals which, if moderate to severely affected, they can’t access</span></li><li style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 59pt; padding-left:13pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Poor communication between services that are provided unless the family is fortunate enough to be in an area with a specialist services (only 8 in England – cut from 11)</span></li><li style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 59pt; padding-left:13pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Children and families are still faced with threats of safeguarding proceedings where there is no specialist support</span></li><li style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 59pt; padding-left:13pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">40% of those who finally</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">get to a clinic</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">have been mis</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">diagnosed</span></li></ol><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 144pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ol start="3" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; list-style-position:inside; margin:0pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">ME/CFS is the main cause of long-term school absence yet children are not able to access the care pathways, services and treatment provided to children with other long-term conditions. </span></li></ol><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ol start="4" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; list-style-position:inside; margin:0pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Prognosis for children is vastly improved if diagnosed correctly and promptly – this is not happening.</span></li></ol><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ol start="5" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; list-style-position:inside; margin:0pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">A</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">wareness</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> in schools </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">needs to be raised </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">and education and health services need to work together to ensure the estimated 33,000 children and young people (1/100 children in secondary schools) are picked up early and the correct information provided. Where this has been implemented it has been effective but </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger